data.description: Welcome home! This inviting split foyer at 227 Daniel Springs Court in Villa Rica, Georgia features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a spacious bonus room in the finished basement. Coming through the front door, your living room is situated at the center of the home and is adorned with a fireplace, perfect for cozying up after a long day. The newly renovated, modern kitchen boasts beautiful quartz countertops, a sleek black tile backsplash, and white tile flooring. Kitchen appliances are included. Off from your kitchen, you will find a back deck overlooking the backyard. Perfect for grilling and entertaining. Offset from your living area, you will find a spacious master bedroom offering plenty of natural light and tray ceilings accompanied by a private and newly renovated master bathroom. On the opposite end of your living area, you will find 2 bedrooms situated on either side of the second and newly remodeled bathroom. Coming down your stairs into the basement is a large bonus room that could be used as a playroom, den, office, theatre, or extra bedroom. To the right of the stairs is a spacious 2-car garage offering plenty of storage space. Venturing outside, this home is nestled on a corner lot with a partially fenced backyard, perfect for pets, and offers both privacy and space. Ideally located 8 minutes from I-20 and 40 minutes from Atlanta, this home seamlessly combines comfort and convenience. Located in a USDA-eligible area. Schedule your showing today and see the charm of this house for yourself.
